{"type":"message","id":"897b81c3","parentId":"4ceed93c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:28:50.135Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978 空闲检测自主学习] 请检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）。如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息），则执行自主学习：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n如果有活跃对话，直接回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 6:28 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 22:28 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775082530130}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7cb4141","parentId":"897b81c3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:28:54.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that's checking for idle conditions and then potentially doing self-learning. I need to:\n1. First check sessions_list to see if there's an active conversation in the last 5 minutes\n2. If no active conversation, search for industry news and save learning notes\n\nLet me check sessions_list first.","thinkingSignature":"d2a862e7739ce7e51af6ebc2b894c13afa88440618f259b0740dcbf2f1785bb9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hy5jzgtatkvy_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":103,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":44393,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0001236,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0.00002064,"total":0.00150477}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775082530132}}
